132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST REGULAR SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 459
S.P. 192 In Senate, February 11, 2025
Provider Services
Received by the Secretary of the Senate on February 5, 2025. Referred to the Committee
on Health Coverage, Insurance and Financial Services pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered
printed.
DAREK M. GRANT
Secretary of the Senate
Presented by Senator CURRY of Waldo.
Printed on recycled paper
1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 CONCEPT DRAFT
3 SUMMARY
44 This bill is a concept draft pursuant to Joint Rule 208.
5 This bill proposes to regulate the use of prior authorization for health care provider
6 services.
